title: India Launches New Space Mission
content: ISRO successfully launches Chandrayaan-4 mission to study lunar south pole. Mission aims to support future human missions.

title: Government Announces Digital Infrastructure Plan
content: Ministry of IT announces new digital infrastructure investment plan targeting rural areas. Budget allocation: Rs 50,000 crore.

title: Tech Industry Growth Report
content: India tech sector grows 25% YoY. Startup ecosystem valued at $150 billion. Leading sectors: fintech, healthtech, edtech.
